us in her life."), mdx("p", null, "She is now gone. What remains is an open pack of her rawhide chew bones, her body harness, and her bed. The wonderful memories with her persist.\xA0 Johnny's demise is my greatest loss in life. Though the scriptures aren't explicit about it, I still believe that God will restore our beloved pets in heaven. His great love for us renders highly, this possibility."), mdx("p", null, "Johnny basking in the sunshine at Gyaneswor. Nov 24, 2014"), mdx("p", null, "Glimpses of Johnny:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
